---

### 🟡 8. No Centralized Error Handling

There is no global error handler. Unhandled errors in Express will leak stack traces to the client by default, exposing internal implementation details.

**OWASP:** A05 – Security Misconfiguration

**Recommendation:** Add an error-handling middleware **last**, after all routes:
```js
